# 01-Feb-1999:  Modify default move positions
#		Modify controller settings
# 21-May-1999:  Changed max tilt for two point chop to 3600
# 30-May-1999:  Added RCS Id
#               Added zStepLimit and tiltStepLimit for follow
#
